<msbt attribsize="8">
	<message label="001" attrib="00 00 00 00 00 00 00 00"><tag a="60" b="20" /></message>
	<message label="001_01" attrib="00 00 00 00 00 00 00 00"><anim id="FaintSmile" target="actor" targetSpec="" />即使是在户外非常危险的虫子，<delay8 />
<anim id="Nodding" target="actor" targetSpec="" />来到这里也可以好好地观察了。<tag a="110" b="6" />。</message>
	<message label="001_02" attrib="00 00 00 00 00 00 00 00">一旦去关注虫子的生活，<delay20 />
<anim id="Nodding" target="actor" targetSpec="" />它们好像告诉在告诉我，无论是哪个世界，
<anim id="WrySmile" target="actor" targetSpec="" />都有各自的艰辛……<tag a="110" b="6" />。</message>
	<message label="001_03" attrib="00 00 00 00 00 00 00 00"><anim id="QuestionMark" target="actor" targetSpec="" />你难道不觉得<delay8 />虫子的
造型都很奇特吗？<pageBreak /><anim id="EmotEnd" target="actor" targetSpec="" />要是长时间仔细观察它们，<delay20 />
<anim id="Thinking" target="actor" targetSpec="" />就会不由自主地<delay8 />陷入沉思，<delay20 />
<anim id="Worried" target="actor" targetSpec="" />“究竟为什么会长成这样呢”……<tag a="110" b="6" />。</message>
	<message label="002" attrib="00 00 00 00 00 00 00 00"><tag a="60" b="20" /></message>
	<message label="002_01" attrib="00 00 00 00 00 00 00 00"><anim id="Explain" target="actor" targetSpec="" />这个温室<delay8 />再现了
虫子们生活的环境，<delay8 /><anim id="FaintSmile" target="actor" targetSpec="" />真的很棒。<pageBreak /><anim id="ShyBoy" target="actor" targetSpec="" /><colour id="3" />傅达<colour id="65535" />他好像<delay20 />不太擅长应对虫子，<delay20 />
<anim id="EmotEnd" target="actor" targetSpec="" />但他不会将个人好恶带入工作，<delay20 />
<anim id="Nodding" target="actor" targetSpec="" />真不愧是专业人士。<tag a="110" b="6" />。</message>
	<message label="002_02" attrib="00 00 00 00 00 00 00 00"><anim id="Hot" target="actor" targetSpec="" />一直身处这个温室中，<delay8 />
的确是会觉得有些热<tag a="110" b="0" /><delay20 />
<anim id="EmotEnd" target="actor" targetSpec="" />不过，<delay20 /><anim id="WrySmile" target="actor" targetSpec="" />虫子们精力十足那就好。<tag a="110" b="6" />。</message>
	<message label="002_03" attrib="00 00 00 00 00 00 00 00"><anim id="Explain" target="actor" targetSpec="" />这个展览室<delay20 />是不是很有林中小道的感觉？<delay frames="40" />
<anim id="FaintSmile" target="actor" targetSpec="" />在这里能够尽情观察<delay8 />
虫子们自然生活的情况，<anim id="Hello" target="actor" targetSpec="" /><delay8 />真棒。<tag a="110" b="6" />。</message>
	<message label="003" attrib="00 00 00 00 00 00 00 00"><tag a="60" b="20" /></message>
	<message label="003_01" attrib="00 00 00 00 00 00 00 00"><anim id="Smiling" target="actor" targetSpec="" />这里四季如春，<delay8 />
还开着许多漂亮的小花……<delay frames="40" />
<anim id="Nodding" target="actor" targetSpec="" />一看就能感受到对虫子们的细微照料。<pageBreak /><anim id="FaintSmile" target="actor" targetSpec="" />能在这里被展出的虫子们<anim id="Hello" target="actor" targetSpec="" /><delay8 />
都挺幸福的呀。<tag a="110" b="6" />。</message>
	<message label="003_02" attrib="00 00 00 00 00 00 00 00"><anim id="FaintSmile" target="actor" targetSpec="" />不觉得这个温室很漂亮吗？<delay frames="40" />
<anim id="Nodding" target="actor" targetSpec="" />来观察虫子固然是不错，<delay20 />
<anim id="Explain" target="actor" targetSpec="" />但这里也是很棒的散步地点哦。<pageBreak /><anim id="Blushing" target="actor" targetSpec="" />多看看美丽的事物，<delay8 />
身心都会变得更加洁净<tag a="110" b="0" /><delay8 />
<anim id="BigSmile" target="actor" targetSpec="" />我一直是这么考虑的。<tag a="110" b="6" />。<anim id="FaintSmile" target="actor" targetSpec="" /></message>
	<message label="003_03" attrib="00 00 00 00 00 00 00 00"><anim id="FaintSmile" target="actor" targetSpec="" />我个人是非常喜欢<delay8 /><anim id="Hello" target="actor" targetSpec="" />这个温室的。<delay frames="40" />
<anim id="EmotEnd" target="actor" targetSpec="" /><colour id="3" />傅达<colour id="65535" />的品位<tag a="110" b="0" /><delay8 />
<anim id="Thinking" target="actor" targetSpec="" />看来不可小觑啊<tag a="110" b="0" /><tag a="110" b="6" />。</message>
	<message label="100" attrib="00 00 00 00 00 00 00 00"><tag a="60" b="20" /></message>
	<message label="100_01" attrib="00 00 00 00 00 00 00 00"><anim id="FaintSmile" target="actor" targetSpec="" />感谢你特意拜访<delay8 />
这座<tag a="110" b="32" />上的<anim id="Greeting" target="actor" targetSpec="" /><delay8 /><colour id="1" />博物馆<colour id="65535" />！<pageBreak /><anim id="EmotEnd" target="actor" targetSpec="" />机会难得，也请你和虫子们<delay8 />
<anim id="Hello" target="actor" targetSpec="" />度过一段难忘的时光吧！<tag a="110" b="6" />。</message>
	<message label="100_02" attrib="00 00 00 00 00 00 00 00">你……<anim id="Hello" target="actor" targetSpec="" /><delay8 />喜欢虫子吗？<delay frames="50" />
<anim id="EmotEnd" target="actor" targetSpec="" />如果时间充裕的话，希望你一定要去<delay20 />
<anim id="FaintSmile" target="actor" targetSpec="" />看看展出的虫子哦。<tag a="110" b="6" />。</message>
	<message label="100_03" attrib="00 00 00 00 00 00 00 00"><anim id="FaintSmile" target="actor" targetSpec="" /><tag a="110" b="33" />上的<anim id="Hello" target="actor" targetSpec="" /><delay8 /><colour id="1" />博物馆<colour id="65535" />怎么样？<delay frames="40" />
<anim id="EmotEnd" target="actor" targetSpec="" />比如这间虫类展览室，<delay20 />
<anim id="ShyBoy" target="actor" targetSpec="" />我个人觉得应该算是挺不错的。<tag a="110" b="6" />。</message>
	<message label="200" attrib="00 00 00 00 00 00 00 00"><tag a="60" b="20" /></message>
	<message label="200_01" attrib="00 00 00 00 00 00 00 00"><anim id="HappyDance" target="actor" targetSpec="" />这座<tag a="110" b="32" />上能建成<delay20 />
如此气派的<colour id="1" />博物馆<colour id="65535" />，真令人欣喜呀。<pageBreak /><anim id="Hello" target="actor" targetSpec="" />虫类展览室也独具匠心，<delay20 />
<anim id="Nodding" target="actor" targetSpec="" />在这里的话，<delay8 />
不管多久都能待下去。<tag a="110" b="6" />。</message>
	<message label="200_02" attrib="00 00 00 00 00 00 00 00"><anim id="Smiling" target="actor" targetSpec="" />我在这座刚建成的<colour id="1" />博物馆<colour id="65535" />里<delay8 />
四处转了转，<delay20 />
像是在探险一样，真有趣！<pageBreak /><anim id="BigSmile" target="actor" targetSpec="" />特别是这间虫类展览室！<delay20 />
<anim id="HappyDance" target="actor" targetSpec="" />让我有一种回归童心的感觉呢。<tag a="110" b="6" />。</message>
	<message label="200_03" attrib="00 00 00 00 00 00 00 00"><anim id="BigSmile" target="actor" targetSpec="" />终于这座<tag a="110" b="32" />上也有<colour id="1" />博物馆<colour id="65535" />了呀！<delay20 />
<anim id="HappyFlower" target="actor" targetSpec="" />而且，<delay8 />竟然还是这么一栋有派头的建筑！<pageBreak /><anim id="FaintSmile" target="actor" targetSpec="" />你不觉得这间虫类展览室很是绝妙？<delay20 />
<anim id="Love" target="actor" targetSpec="" />我只看了一眼就喜欢上了呢。<tag a="110" b="6" />。</message>
</msbt>